prop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color=
: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bord=
er-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #cc=
c;">talked in 2021</a> about an equity line of credit that Yorkville did fo=
r Lordstown Motors Corp., another recent SPAC company. And this week Bloomb=
erg=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/3609=
1809.196395/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDc=
tMTYvdHJ1bXAtbWVkaWEtdGFwcy1vYnNjdXJlLXNwYWMtZnJpZW5kbHktbmV3LWplcnNleS1mdW=
