border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">eligibility requiremen=
ts for Form S-3</a> include that the registrant has been public for at leas=
t 12 calendar months. And <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/36091809.196395/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmFrZXJib3R0cy5jb20vdGhvdWdodC1sZWF=
