xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">the SEC i=
nterprets those requirements</a> to mean that a de-SPAC company can=E2=80=
=99t use Form S-3 for 12 months after the de-SPAC merger. <a href=3D"https:=
